Interface PVDcBus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Bus, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, DcBus, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PVDcBusImpl

    public interface PVDcBus
extends DcBus
    A representation of the model object 'PV Dc Bus'. Bus concept for PV analysis and simulation

    The following features are supported:

    • Pv Module
    • Inverter
